A vintage-style technical illustration depicting a complex mechanical assembly line where raw materials (represented as colorful geometric shapes and data streams) flow through interconnected brass gears, copper pipes, and Victorian-era industrial machinery. On one side, an ornate workbench with craftsman's tools shapes delicate interface components, while on the opposite side, a robust steam-powered engine processes and stores information in glass containers filled with glowing amber liquid. The two sides are connected by an elegant pneumatic tube system carrying small capsules of structured data between them. The scene has warm sepia tones with touches of deep teal and copper highlights, rendered in the style of 19th-century technical patent drawings with cross-hatching and precise linework. Ambient steam rises from various junction points, creating atmospheric depth.
